headline: Q3 Earnings Highlights: Sabre (NASDAQ:SABR) Vs The Rest Of The Travel and Vacation Providers Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how travel and vacation providers stocks fared in Q3, starting with Sabre (NASDAQ:SABR).
